ed-Delivery-Date.png\";s:5:\"title\";s:29:\"Estimated Order Delivery Date\";s:4:\"copy\";s:92:\"Display the Estimated Delivery Date and Time on the Product, Shop, Cart, and Checkout Pages.\";s:11:\"button-text\";s:10:\"Learn More\";s:3:\"url\";s:63:\"https://woocommerce.com/products/estimated-order-delivery-date/\";}i:14;a:8:{s:4:\"slug\";s:45:\"orders-list-empty-body-international-reseller\";s:7:\"context\";s:22:\"orders-list-empty-body\";s:7:\"product\";s:22:\"international-reseller\";s:4:\"icon\";s:67:\"https://woocommerce.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/ir_logo_blue.png\";s:5:\"title\";s:22:\"International Reseller\";s:4:\"copy\";s:247:\"Territory-based access control for WooCommerce. Assign shop managers to specific countries, regions, and languages — they only see their orders, customers, and content. Full HPOS compatibility with support for WPML, Polylang, and TranslatePress.\";s:11:\"button-text\";s:10:\"Learn More\";s:3:\"url\";s:56:\"https://woocommerce.com/products/international-reseller/\";}i:15;a:8:{s:4:\"slug\";s:50:\"orders-list-empty-body-shipment-and-order-tracking\";s:7:\"context\";s:22:\"orders-list-empty-body\";s:7:\"product\";s:27:\"shipment-and-order-tracking\";s:4:\"icon\";s:92:\"https://woocommerce.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Shipment-and-Order-Tracking-160x160-1.png\";s:5:\"title\";s:27:\"Shipment and Order Tracking\";s:4:\"copy\";s:118:\"Share shipment and order status details with your customers, so they can easily track their order and shipment status.\";s:11:\"button-text\";s:10:\"Learn More\";s:3:\"url\";s:61:\"https://woocommerce.com/products/shipment-and-order-tracking/\";}i:16;a:8:{s:4:\"slug\";s:40:\"orders-list-empty-body-local-pickup-plus\";s:7:\"context\";s:22:\"orders-list-empty-body\";s:7:\"product\";s:17:\"local-pickup-plus\";s:4:\"icon\";s:78:\"https://woocommerce.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/skyverge-wc-icon-b2vhw6.png\";s:5:\"title\";s:17:\"Local Pickup Plus\";s:4:\"copy\";s:135:\"Let customers buy online and pick up in