(15, 1, '2026-03-29 21:56:05', '2026-03-29 21:56:05', '<p data-start=\"140\" data-end=\"471\">“Introduction to Programming for Dummies” is a beginner-friendly guide designed to simplify the world of coding for first-time learners. Written in a clear and engaging style, the book breaks down complex programming concepts into easy-to-understand explanations, making it ideal for students with little to no prior experience.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"765\">With practical examples, step-by-step exercises, and a touch of humor, this book aims to build confidence while developing a strong foundation in programming principles. Perfect for university students and self-learners looking to start their coding journey without feeling overwhelmed.</p>', 'Introduction to Programming for Dummies', '', 'trash', 'open', 'closed', '', 'introduction-to-programming-for-dummies__trashed', '', '', '2026-03-30 23:17:48', '2026-03-30 23:17:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bookshop/?post_type=product&#038;p=15', 0, 'product', '', 0),
