(35, 1, '2026-03-30 00:00:48', '2026-03-30 00:00:48', '<p data-start=\"213\" data-end=\"270\"><strong data-start=\"213\" data-end=\"270\">A powerful story of identity, trauma, and redemption.</strong></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"272\" data-end=\"423\"><em data-start=\"272\" data-end=\"280\">Flight</em> by <span class=\"hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline\"><span class=\"whitespace-normal\">Sherman Alexie</span></span> follows Zits, a troubled teenage boy caught between anger, abandonment, and a search for belonging.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"425\" data-end=\"664\">After a violent incident, Zits is mysteriously transported through time, living the lives of different people across American history. Through these experiences, he is forced to confront pain, violence, and the consequences of his actions.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr data-start=\"666\" data-end=\"669\" />\r\n\r\n<h3 data-section-id=\"1mdoose\" data-start=\"671\" data-end=\"689\">✨ Key Features</h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"690\" data-end=\"880\">\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"hxyeiq\" data-start=\"690\" data-end=\"754\">Unique concept: <strong data-start=\"708\" data-end=\"752\">time travel through different identities</strong></li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"1fumma4\" data-start=\"755\" data-end=\"805\">Explores <strong data-start=\"766\" data-end=\"803\">trauma, identity, and forgiveness</strong></li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"17n1llt\" data-start=\"806\" data-end=\"851\">Thought-provoking and emotionally intense</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"118auie\" data-start=\"852\" data-end=\"880\">Short but impactful read</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr data-start=\"882\" data-end=\"885\" />\r\n\r\n<h3 data-section-id=\"1tetnml\" data-start=\"887\" data-end=\"905\">🎯 Perfect for</h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"906\" data-end=\"1019\">\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"10vf4xj\" data-start=\"906\" data-end=\"931\">Teen to adult readers</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"1q4egg6\" data-start=\"932\" data-end=\"972\">Fans of <strong data-start=\"942\" data-end=\"970\">deep, reflective fiction</strong></li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"x0pji9\" data-start=\"973\" data-end=\"1019\">Readers interested in history and identity</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr data-start=\"1021\" data-end=\"1024\" />\r\n\r\n<h3 data-section-id=\"1c1hc5w\" data-start=\"1026\" data-end=\"1048\">📦 Product Details</h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1049\" data-end=\"1184\">\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"1q6qh05\" data-start=\"1049\" data-end=\"1075\">Author: Sherman Alexie</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"1z0eds3\" data-start=\"1076\" data-end=\"1128\">Genre: Contemporary Fiction / Historical Fiction</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"fh1ks1\" data-start=\"1129\" data-end=\"1162\">Format: Paperback / Hardcover</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"1lp14du\" data-start=\"1163\" data-end=\"1184\">Language: English</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Flight', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'flight', '', '', '2026-03-31 11:05:04', '2026-03-31 11:05:04', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bookshop/?post_type=product&#038;p=35', 0, 'product', '', 0),
