(60, 1, '2026-03-30 22:32:28', '2026-03-30 22:32:28', '<p data-start=\"256\" data-end=\"332\"><strong data-start=\"256\" data-end=\"332\">A comprehensive and trusted guide to mastering university-level physics.</strong></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"334\" data-end=\"515\"><em data-start=\"334\" data-end=\"354\">University Physics</em> by <span class=\"hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline\"><span class=\"whitespace-normal\">Hugh D. Young</span></span> and <span class=\"hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline\"><span class=\"whitespace-normal\">Roger A. Freedman</span></span> is one of the most widely used physics textbooks in universities worldwide.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"517\" data-end=\"764\">Designed for students in science and engineering, the book provides clear explanations of core physics concepts—from mechanics and thermodynamics to electromagnetism and modern physics—supported by detailed examples and problem-solving techniques.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr data-start=\"766\" data-end=\"769\" />\r\n\r\n<h3 data-section-id=\"1mdoose\" data-start=\"771\" data-end=\"789\">✨ Key Features</h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"790\" data-end=\"997\">\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"moe1a4\" data-start=\"790\" data-end=\"840\">Covers <strong data-start=\"799\" data-end=\"838\">full undergraduate physics syllabus</strong></li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"epiqlb\" data-start=\"841\" data-end=\"885\">Step-by-step <strong data-start=\"856\" data-end=\"883\">problem-solving methods</strong></li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"172drij\" data-start=\"886\" data-end=\"939\">Includes <strong data-start=\"897\" data-end=\"937\">real-world applications and examples</strong></li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"1p4muv7\" data-start=\"940\" data-end=\"997\">Often comes with <strong data-start=\"959\" data-end=\"995\">practice questions and exercises</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr data-start=\"999\" data-end=\"1002\" />\r\n\r\n<h3 data-section-id=\"1tetnml\" data-start=\"1004\" data-end=\"1022\">🎯 Perfect for</h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1023\" data-end=\"1171\">\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"rxf788\" data-start=\"1023\" data-end=\"1073\">University students (IT, Engineering, Physics)</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"y9xlho\" data-start=\"1074\" data-end=\"1120\">First-year and second-year physics courses</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"183turm\" data-start=\"1121\" data-end=\"1171\">Anyone needing a <strong data-start=\"1140\" data-end=\"1169\">strong physics foundation</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr data-start=\"1173\" data-end=\"1176\" />\r\n\r\n<h3 data-section-id=\"1c1hc5w\" data-start=\"1178\" data-end=\"1200\">📦 Product Details</h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1201\" data-end=\"1367\">\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"1q6khy2\" data-start=\"1201\" data-end=\"1246\">Authors: Hugh D. Young, Roger A. Freedman</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"13ajiz7\" data-start=\"1247\" data-end=\"1286\">Genre: Academic / Science / Physics</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"1k6pldl\" data-start=\"1287\" data-end=\"1311\">Level: Undergraduate</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"fh1ks1\" data-start=\"1312\" data-end=\"1345\">Format: Paperback / Hardcover</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"1lp14du\" data-start=\"1346\" data-end=\"1367\">Language: English</li>\r\n</ul>', 'University Physics — Hugh D. Young & Freedman', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'university-physics-hugh-d-young-freedman', '', '', '2026-03-30 22:33:12', '2026-03-30 22:33:12', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bookshop/?post_type=product&#038;p=60', 0, 'product', '', 0),
