(79, 1, '2026-03-30 22:59:57', '2026-03-30 22:59:57', '<p data-start=\"232\" data-end=\"296\"><strong data-start=\"232\" data-end=\"296\">A clear and authoritative introduction to the immune system.</strong></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"298\" data-end=\"465\"><em data-start=\"298\" data-end=\"328\">Roitt’s Essential Immunology</em> by <span class=\"hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline\"><span class=\"whitespace-normal\">Peter J. Delves</span></span> is one of the most widely used textbooks for understanding how the human immune system works.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"467\" data-end=\"689\">It explains key concepts such as immune cells, antibodies, antigens, and immune responses, while also covering diseases, vaccines, and clinical applications—making it a strong foundation for medical and biological studies.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr data-start=\"691\" data-end=\"694\" />\r\n\r\n<h3 data-section-id=\"1mdoose\" data-start=\"696\" data-end=\"714\">✨ Key Features</h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"715\" data-end=\"949\">\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"1fniqtn\" data-start=\"715\" data-end=\"773\">Comprehensive coverage of <strong data-start=\"743\" data-end=\"771\">core immunology concepts</strong></li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"l0u4ju\" data-start=\"774\" data-end=\"826\">Clear diagrams of <strong data-start=\"794\" data-end=\"824\">immune processes and cells</strong></li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"1f8gbxr\" data-start=\"827\" data-end=\"893\">Links theory to <strong data-start=\"845\" data-end=\"870\">clinical applications</strong> (diseases, vaccines)</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"k90dr2\" data-start=\"894\" data-end=\"949\">Widely used in <strong data-start=\"911\" data-end=\"947\">medical and life science courses</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr data-start=\"951\" data-end=\"954\" />\r\n\r\n<h3 data-section-id=\"1tetnml\" data-start=\"956\" data-end=\"974\">🎯 Perfect for</h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"975\" data-end=\"1098\">\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"1ag4iyw\" data-start=\"975\" data-end=\"1007\">Medical and nursing students</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"1dkhoea\" data-start=\"1008\" data-end=\"1046\">Biology and biotechnology students</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"ch2bri\" data-start=\"1047\" data-end=\"1098\">Anyone studying <strong data-start=\"1065\" data-end=\"1096\">immunology or human biology</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr data-start=\"1100\" data-end=\"1103\" />\r\n\r\n<h3 data-section-id=\"1c1hc5w\" data-start=\"1105\" data-end=\"1127\">📦 Product Details</h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1128\" data-end=\"1314\">\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"xtkdoy\" data-start=\"1128\" data-end=\"1174\">Author: Peter J. Delves (and contributors)</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"1ehq8xd\" data-start=\"1175\" data-end=\"1215\">Genre: Academic / Medicine / Biology</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"16x617h\" data-start=\"1216\" data-end=\"1258\">Level: Undergraduate to Medical School</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"fh1ks1\" data-start=\"1259\" data-end=\"1292\">Format: Paperback / Hardcover</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"1lp14du\" data-start=\"1293\" data-end=\"1314\">Language: English</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Roitt’s Essential Immunology', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '79', '', '', '2026-03-30 23:02:18', '2026-03-30 23:02:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bookshop/?post_type=product&#038;p=79', 0, 'product', '', 0),
