(86, 1, '2026-03-30 23:16:35', '2026-03-30 23:16:35', '<p data-start=\"1562\" data-end=\"1612\"><strong data-start=\"1562\" data-end=\"1612\">Power, betrayal, and a dangerous game of love.</strong></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1614\" data-end=\"1778\"><em data-start=\"1614\" data-end=\"1632\">The Cruel Prince</em> by <span class=\"hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline\"><span class=\"whitespace-normal\">Holly Black</span></span> follows Jude, a mortal girl living in the treacherous High Court of Faerie, where humans are despised.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1780\" data-end=\"1928\">Determined to gain power and belong, Jude must navigate political schemes, deception, and her complicated relationship with the cruel Prince Cardan.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr data-start=\"1930\" data-end=\"1933\" />\r\n\r\n<h3 data-section-id=\"1mdoose\" data-start=\"1935\" data-end=\"1953\">✨ Key Features</h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1954\" data-end=\"2104\">\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"8h4l4l\" data-start=\"1954\" data-end=\"1999\">Political fantasy with <strong data-start=\"1979\" data-end=\"1997\">court intrigue</strong></li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"iv1kby\" data-start=\"2000\" data-end=\"2041\">Popular <strong data-start=\"2010\" data-end=\"2039\">enemies-to-lovers dynamic</strong></li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"cj1w35\" data-start=\"2042\" data-end=\"2064\">Strong female lead</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"blii7t\" data-start=\"2065\" data-end=\"2104\">First book in a bestselling trilogy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2109\" />\r\n\r\n<h3 data-section-id=\"1tetnml\" data-start=\"2111\" data-end=\"2129\">🎯 Perfect for</h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"2130\" data-end=\"2239\">\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"d9n4tt\" data-start=\"2130\" data-end=\"2157\">Fantasy romance readers</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"1seh4lx\" data-start=\"2158\" data-end=\"2206\">Fans of drama, power struggles, and strategy</li>\r\n 	<li data-section-id=\"mye5gt\" data-start=\"2